Lufthansa Plans Sale or Break-Up of BMI, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   B r o w n i n g
-- 
2011-09-11T05:30:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-11/lufthansa-plans-sale-or-break-up-of-bmi-sunday-times-reports.html
Deutsche Lufthansa AG (LHA)  appointed
Morgan Stanley to advise on the sale or break-up of U.K. airline
BMI, the Sunday Times reported, without saying where it got the
information.  Lufthansa may sell BMI as a whole or through its units, BMI
Baby and BMI Regional, the newspaper said. BMI is exploring
various options with Lufthansa and no decision has been taken,
the Sunday Times reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Browning in London at 
 jbrowning9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Kenneth Wong  at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  